---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Mesh Belt Conveyor Furnace Atmosphere Control Kits" description="You operate continuous production lines where uptime is the most critical factor. Our atmosphere control kits for mesh belt furnaces provide stable liquid feeding and gas distribution.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Furnace Application Solutions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8 leading-tight">Mesh Belt Conveyor Furnace Atmosphere Control Kits</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 mb-12">
        <p>You operate continuous production lines where uptime is the most critical factor for your profitability. Our atmosphere control kits for mesh belt furnaces are engineered to provide stable liquid feeding and precise gas distribution across the entire conveyor length. You will minimize oxidation and ensure uniform case hardening for high-volume parts by integrating our specialized drip feeders and recording instruments into your line.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Technical Challenge</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Continuous mesh belt lines require high consistency in gas distribution. Fluctuations lead to uneven hardness in your parts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Weigu Solution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Weigu provides multi-point drip feeding and atmospheric probes. You gain precise control over the entire heating zone, ensuring high yield.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Components For This Application</h2>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Precision Drip Feeders</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Atmosphere Probes</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> High-Temp Sensors</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Thermal Insulation Fixings</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <CTA title="Optimize Your Mesh Belt Process Today" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
